ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectAgri-Recovery - Agricultural producers in the Prairie Provinces and Quebec
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to provide assistance through the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program under the AgriRecovery Framework to assist agricultural producers in the Prairie Provinces and Quebec manage the impacts of excess moisture and flooding in the spring/summer of 2011.
